<HEADLINE>
FT  24 MAY 94 / International Capital Markets: Enskilda in Asian venture
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By ANTONIA SHARPE
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Enskilda Corporate, the merchant banking division of Sweden's Skandinaviska
Enskilda Banken, has set up a partnership with Crosby Financial Holdings, an
independent Asian merchant banking firm, to provide Asian investment advice
and services in Sweden, Norway and Finland, writes Antonia Sharpe.
Under the arrangements, Enskilda will assume exclusive responsibility for
dis-tributing Crosby's equity research in Sweden, Norway and Finland.
