<HEADLINE>
FT  23 MAY 94 / International Company News: Greek Banking and Finance Survey
 -Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The figures for assets, deposits and loans held by Greece's biggest banks in
1992 in the above survey (May 20) should have been stated in drachmas and
not dollars.
</TEXT>
